{"TopicId":218340,"ForumId":200,"TopicTitle":"Flags are not persistant","CreatedByName":"Rubenio","CreatedById":217946,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-10T23:56:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Rubenio","CreatedById":217946,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-10T23:56:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.1.3.1 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 11 Pro 64-bit (10.0, Build 22621) | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-10700F CPU @ 2.90GHz (16 CPUs), ~2.9GHz | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E49152MB RAM\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen planting a flag on either Mun or Minmus - after the vessel is returned home and recovered, there are no flags remaining.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was a tech support thread back in Feb, but it appears this is still a bug. here is a link to that thread.\u00A0 i can confirm that this is still happening and i am posting it here in case this was not correctly posted before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002264088\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9499203307\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/212765-flags-are-not-persistant/?do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:171px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-07-11T02:26:30Z\u0022 title=\u002207/11/2023 02:26  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 11, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Anth12\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-11T02:42:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can confirm, I had\u00A0 this bug several times on different saves where I get the \u0022ksp default\u0022 flag when I never selected it:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022374gO3s.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/374gO3s.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022t05Yau9.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/t05Yau9.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DylanSP","CreatedById":230126,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-08-02T22:40:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan confirm. I\u0027ve planted multiple flags on multiple celestial bodies, not just Mun and Minmus, and none of them ever show up on the map or tracking station.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-08-02T22:51:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224308171\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022218340\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221691016011\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022230126\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DylanSP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, DylanSP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan confirm. I\u0027ve planted multiple flags on multiple celestial bodies, not just Mun and Minmus, and none of them ever show up on the map or tracking station.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey don\u0027t show up on the map or tracking station but they still exist.\u003Cbr\u003E\nHowever, there is another problem where the flag won\u0027t be visible if you cross from one \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E to another \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E which is countered by saving and loading within the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESOI\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}